      <title>Hey everyone! Long time no see ;). We love &amp; miss you all…but this post goes out...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DOvmx-lkQqH/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/550604651_820044850585930_561012738242275647_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=105&amp;ig_cache_key=MzcyNDM2NTk3NzA4MjcyNzA0Nw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjY0MHgzNjAuc2RyLkMzIn0%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=Z-I7Of7LpHYQ7kNvwF2wowD&amp;_nc_oc=AdrpVbKhIrxt3K1SkTKsAnSZy0hiTZMDexFkx90VKzPE8KObTfuICt5Q9lea0Jkmoro&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=if4D0IoLibrR38aXxDtO0A&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwwaMFsjwXxLX37ceabq9hQ6mzxkVBEHIe7Z1aDSnB5cQ&amp;oe=69C8F283" alt="Instagram billede fra @biggypop" /></p><p><strong>@biggypop</strong></p><p>Hey everyone! Long time no see ;). We love &amp; miss you all…but this post goes out extra special, to our Aussie friends. See, it’s just about time for the 3rd annual, Wild Aid benefit concert…and we wanna make sure that the good peeps of Brisbane, the Gold Coast, and Byron Bay areas, know what’s up. September 27th, 2025 is the date, and the Green Room, Byron Bay, is the place. The event’s proceeds will support the Byron Bay Wildlife Hospital and their lifesaving care of sick, injured, and orphaned Australian native animals. Basically all my feathered cousins, but also my furry and scaly friends too :).<br/>
The Hoodoo Gurus, who you’ve been listening to in this post, will be headlining, and there will be performances by Toni Childs, Screamfeeder, and the Honey Sliders, as well. Get your tix now! The link to moshtix.com.au (something, something, Wild Aid) etc., is in my bio at the top. That’s the easiest way. Just click on the link up there. Thanks a bunch everyone! ❤️ #BiggyPop #IggyPop #WildAid #ByronBayWildLifeHospital #ForTheWildLife #HoodooGurus #ByronBay #Brisbane #GoldCoast #Australia #Moluccan #Cockatoos #Birds #Roos #Koalas #Wallaby #Wombat  Song: ‘Where Nowhere Is’ by Hoodoo Gurus</p>]]></description>
