The Hoodoo Gurus, who you’ve been listening to in this post, will be headlining, and there will be performances by Toni Childs, Screamfeeder, and the Honey Sliders, as well. Get your tix now! The link to moshtix.com.au (something, something, Wild Aid) etc., is in my bio at the top. That’s the easiest way. Just click on the link up there. Thanks a bunch everyone! ❤️ #BiggyPop #IggyPop #WildAid #ByronBayWildLifeHospital #ForTheWildLife #HoodooGurus #ByronBay #Brisbane #GoldCoast #Australia #Moluccan #Cockatoos #Birds #Roos #Koalas #Wallaby #Wombat  Song: ‘Where Nowhere Is’ by Hoodoo Gurus</p>]]></content:encoded>
